  <summary date="2021-08-31T14:24:50Z" status="Introduced in House">Upskilling and Retraining Assistance Act

This bill increases to $12,000 in 2021-2022, the exclusion from employee gross income, for income tax purposes, of employer-paid educational assistance programs.

The bill also expands the exclusion to include amounts paid for education-related tools and technology (e.g., hand tools, computers, software, licensure fees).</summary>
